Process Enactment Tool(PET) enables efficient, and easy management of projects:

- Allows task estimation

- Easy tracking of progress

- Customizable as per user needs

Technologies used:
Ruby (1.8.7)
Rails (2.3)

The project was developed as part of a course Foundation of Software Engineering(96-700) at CMU-SV. Extreme Programming practices like:
- Test Driven Development
- Pair Programming
- Continuous Integration
- Incremental Development
, were implemented throughout its development.